宫北草坪进行了清场，记者们被告知需迅速进入白宫新闻简报室。 由于枪声，白宫处于封锁状态，白宫周边出现大量警力部署。 一名特勤局官员透露，该机构正在调查关于西北区第 17 街与宾夕法尼亚大道交汇处发生枪击事件的报告，该地点紧邻白宫建筑群的外部区域。 另据了解，美国联邦调查局表示，联邦调查局警员已赶赴现场，并正协助特勤局应对白宫周边区域发生枪击事件的情况，将在条件允许时向公众发布最新信息。美国白宫附近传出枪声 周边出现大量警力部署"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-036f6754a283c2466a354801ac114bc2_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "64 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2041783305054285850"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIpduBpamht8c1EAMaCTExOTY0MTUxOSDC8cjQBjAAOOgBQBNyEzIwNDE3ODMzMDUwNTQyODU4NTB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1779611378.987175", "card_id": "Q_2041600955062251689", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 28}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "苏超第四轮，淮安 0 比 1 盐城、宿迁 1 比 2 南通、连云港 1 比 3 徐州，比赛有哪些亮点？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": " "}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-b798bd39dbfb986e829a2f0a4dbbe00a_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "62 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2041600955062251689"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIpduBpamht8c1EAMaCTExOTYzNjE2NiDuncbQBjAAOCdAFHITMjA0MTYwMDk1NTA2MjI1MTY4OXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1779611378.987875", "card_id": "Q_296041334", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 213}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价盗月社食遇记？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-1eaa32d7619107b3f69a474e3b5cd7d4_1440w.webp"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": 